-- Euro Weakens Versus Dollar, Yen; Depreciates 0.3% to $1.2246
-- B y   D a v i d   G o o d m a n
-- 2012-07-27T08:53:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-27/euro-weakens-versus-dollar-yen-depreciates-0-3-to-1-2246.html
The euro declined against the dollar
and the yen, reversing earlier gains.  The 17-nation shared currency dropped 0.3 percent to
$1.2246 as of 9:50 a.m. London time, after earlier gaining as
much as 0.3 percent to $1.2315.  It was 0.4 percent weaker at 95.66 yen after advancing as
much as 0.5 percent to 96.51.  To contact the reporter on this story:
